OL,3,CPupils at academy school chain to have
OL,4,Csmartphone access removed
OL,6,FPupils at a chain of academy schools
OL,7,Fin England are to have access to
OL,8,Fsmartphones removed.
OL,10,FThe Ormiston Academies Trust is
OL,11,Fbringing in the rules during the
OL,12,Fschool day due to the "overwhelming"
OL,13,Frelationship between their use and
OL,14,Fmental health, according to chief
OL,15,Fexecutive Tom Rees.
OL,17,FHe told The Guardian the trust was
OL,18,F"seeing huge and real concerns" about
OL,19,Fpupils' mental health with a "clear
OL,20,Fcorrelation" between those issue and
OL,21,Fthe use of phones and social media.
