OL,6,F"Not all mobile phone use is equal and
OL,7,Fthe relationship between that and
OL,8,Fadolescent mental health, we think, is
OL,9,Foverwhelming," he said.
OL,11,F"There is a responsibility for society
OL,12,Fto respond and a responsibility for
OL,13,Fschools to make it harder for children
OL,14,Fto access inappropriate content
OL,15,Fthrough the school day and restrict
OL,16,Fthe draw of social media."
