OL,6,FMr Rees said "a battle for focus and
OL,7,Fconcentration" to help learning was
OL,8,Fone of the reasons behind the move
OL,9,Fwith pupils thinking about any
OL,10,Fnotifications on their phones.
OL,12,F"That is impacting young people's
OL,13,Fability to learn, to retain
OL,14,Finformation, to concentrate, to
OL,15,Ffocus," he said. "An increasing
OL,16,Fdistraction is catastrophic for the
OL,17,Fprocess of learning, and that's true
OL,18,Fboth at school and at home."
