OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, the Australian government
OL,12,Fpromised to introduce legislation this
OL,13,Fyear to enforce a minimum age for
OL,14,Fchildren to access social media.
OL,16,FPrime Minister Anthony Albanese said
OL,17,Fthe government would soon trial age
OL,18,Fverification technology with a view to
OL,19,Fbanning children from opening social
OL,20,Fmedia accounts. The line would be
OL,21,Fdrawn between the ages of 14 and 16.
