OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Peter Kyle said
OL,7,Fhe was "looking very closely at the
OL,8,FAustralian experience".
OL,10,FIn February, the Department for
OL,11,FEducation (DfE) issued guidance which
OL,12,Fsaid "we owe it to our children to do
OL,13,Fwhat we can to remove distractions and
OL,14,Fenable them to be fully present and
OL,15,Fengaged in the classroom".
